Welcome to the Inteligence Quotient Test.
Before starting the test, make sure you are in a place where you can focus.
We will evaluate, through 40 questions, your ability to learn, understand, form concepts, process information, and apply logic and reason.
Your results will be sent to you via email at the end of the test.
The timer will start counting when you press the "Start" button.
